alluxio.worker.file

Class FileSystemWorkerClientServiceHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.worker.file.FileSystemWorkerClientServiceHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AlluxioService.Iface, FileSystemWorkerClientService.Iface

    @NotThreadSafe
public final class FileSystemWorkerClientServiceHandler
extends Object
implements FileSystemWorkerClientService.Iface
    Handles incoming thrift requests from a worker file system client. This is mostly a wrapper around FileSystemWorker and delegates calls to it.
